sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend (AuthModal)
    participant A as AuthContext
    participant S as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as Database (profiles)

    Note over U,DB: === 로그인 흐름 ===
    U->>F: Open AuthModal
    F->>U: Show Email/Password Form
    U->>F: Enter Credentials
    F->>A: signIn(email, password)
    A->>S: signInWithPassword({email, password})
    S->>S: Validate Credentials
    S->>A: Return Session
    A->>A: onAuthStateChange Triggered
    A->>DB: checkAdminRole(userId)
    DB->>A: Return admin status
    A->>DB: checkProfileStatus(userId)
    DB->>A: Return profile (nickname)
    A->>F: Update Auth State
    F->>U: Show Logged In State

    Note over U,DB: === 회원가입 흐름 ===
    U->>F: Switch to Signup Tab
    U->>F: Enter Email, Password, Nickname
    F->>A: signUp(email, password, username)
    A->>S: auth.signUp({email, password, data: {nickname}})
    S->>DB: Create user + profile
    S->>A: Return Success
    A->>F: Update State
    F->>U: Show Success Message
